C-in-CFrance.War Office.Handed in 3.25 p.m6.11.1917.Received 10 p.m.O.A.BG.O.C ..R.F.C. reports to me as follows: -"Fog and low clouds last night and today haveprevented any operations by the Nancy squadron."Secretary,War Cabinet.Circulation for the information of theCabinet.General Staff, War Office,7th November, 1917.
